{
  "video_id": "GAMR5RD_LJo",
  "title": "Barton Seaver: Sustainable seafood? Let's get smart",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "Sustainability represents"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "the what, the where and the how"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "of what is caught."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "The who and the why are what&#39;s important to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "I want to know the people behind my dinner choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "I want to know how I impact them."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "I want to know how they impact me."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "I want to know why they fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "I want to know how they rely on the water&#39;s bounty"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "for their living."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "Understanding all of this enables us"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "to shift our perception of seafood"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "away from a commodity"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "to an opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "to restore our ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "It allows for us to celebrate the seafood"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re also so fortunate to eat."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "So what do we call this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "I think we call it restorative seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 56260.0,
      "text": "Where sustainability is the capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "to endure and maintain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "restorative is the ability to replenish and progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "Restorative seafood allows for an evolving and dynamic system"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "and acknowledges our relationship with the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "as a resource,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "suggesting that we engage to replenish the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "and to encourage its resiliency."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "It is a more hopeful, it is a more human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "and is a more useful way of understanding our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "Wallet guides -- standard issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "by lots in the marine conservation world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "are very handy; they&#39;re a wonderful tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "Green, yellow and red lists [of] seafood species."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "The association is very easy: buy green, don&#39;t buy red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "think twice about yellow."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "But in my mind, it&#39;s really not enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "to just eat green list."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t sustain this without the measure of our success"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "really changing the fate of the species"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "in the yellow and the red."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "But what if we eat only in the green list?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got pole-caught yellowfin tuna here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "comes from sustainable stocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "Pole caught -- no bycatch."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "Great for fishermen. Lots of money. Supporting local economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s a lion of the sea. It&#39;s a top predator."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s the context of this meal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "Am I sitting down in a steakhouse to a 16-ounce portion of this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "Do I do this three times a week?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "I might still be in the green list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m not doing myself, or you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "or the oceans any favors."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "The point is that we have to have a context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "a gauge for our actions in all this."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "Example: I&#39;ve heard that red wine is great for my health --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "antioxidants and minerals -- heart healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s great! I love red wine!"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to drink so much of it. I&#39;m going to be so healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "Well, how many bottles is it"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "before you tell me that I have a problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "Well folks, we have a protein problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "We have lost this sensibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "when it regards our food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "and we are paying a cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "The problem is we are hiding that cost beneath the waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "We are hiding that cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "behind the social acceptance of expanding waistlines."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "And we are hiding that cost behind monster profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "So the first thing about this idea of restorative seafood"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "is that it really takes into account our needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "Restorative seafood might best be represented"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "not by Jaws, or by Flipper, or the Gordon&#39;s fisherman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "but rather, by the Jolly Green Giant."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "Vegetables:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "they might yet save the oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "Sylvia likes to say that blue is the new green."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "Well I&#39;d like to respectfully submit"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "that broccoli green might then be the new blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "We must continue to eat"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "the best seafood possible, if at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "But we also must eat it with a ton of vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "The best part about restorative seafood though"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "is that it comes on the half-shell"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "with a bottle of Tabasco and lemon wedges."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "It comes in a five-ounce portion of tilapia"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "breaded with Dijon mustard and crispy, broiled breadcrumbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "and a steaming pile of pecan quinoa pilaf"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "with crunchy, grilled broccoli"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "so soft and sweet and charred and smoky on the outside"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "with just a hint of chili flake."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "Whooo!"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "This is an easy sell."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "And the best part is all of those ingredients are available"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "to every family at the neighborhood Walmart."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "Jamie Oliver is campaigning"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "to save America from the way we eat."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "Sylvia is campaigning to save the oceans"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "from the way we eat."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a pattern here."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "Forget nuclear holocaust;"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the fork that we have to worry about."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "We have ravaged our Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "and then used the food that we&#39;ve sourced"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "to handicap ourselves in more ways than one."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "So I think we have this whole eating thing wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "And so I think it&#39;s time"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "we change what we expect from our food."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "Sustainability is complicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "but dinner is a reality that we all very much understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s start there."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s been a lot of movement recently in greening our food systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "Dan Barber and Alice Waters"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "are leading passionately the green food Delicious Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "But green foods often represent"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "a way for us to disregard"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "the responsibility as eaters."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "Just because it comes from a green source"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t mean we can treat it with disregard on the plate."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "We have eco-friendly shrimp."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "We can make them; we have that technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "But we can never have any eco-friendly all-you-can-eat shrimp buffet."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "Heart-healthy dinner is a very important part"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "of restorative seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "While we try to manage declining marine populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "the media&#39;s recommending increased consumption of seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "Studies say that tens of thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "of American grandmothers, grandfathers, mothers and fathers"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "might be around for another birthday"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "if we included more seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a reward I am not willing to pass up."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not all about the seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about the way that we look at our plates."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "As a chef, I realize the easiest thing for me to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "is reduce the portion sizes on my plate."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 339260.0,
      "text": "A couple things happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 339260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "I made more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "People started buying appetizers and salads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "because they knew they weren&#39;t going to fill up on the entrees alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "People spent more time engaging in their meals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "engaging with each other over their meals."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "People got, in short, more of what they came there for"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "even though they got less protein."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "They got more calories over the course of a diversified meal."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "They got healthier. I made more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "This is great."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "Environmental consideration was served with every plate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "but it was served with a heaping mound"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "of consideration for human interests at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "One of the other things we did"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "was begin to diversify the species that we served --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "small silverfish, anchovies, mackerel, sardines were uncommon."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "Shellfish, mussels, oysters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "clams, tilapia, char -- these were the common species."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "We were directing tastes"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "towards more resilience, more restorative options."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "This is what we need to favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 395260.0,
      "text": "This is what the green list says."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "But this is also how we can actually begin to restore our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "But what of those big predators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "those fashionable species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "that green list tuna that I was talking about earlier?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "Well, if you must, I have a recipe for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "It pretty much works with any big fish in the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "so here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 415260.0,
      "text": "Start with a 16-ounce portion of big fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 415260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "Get a knife. Cut it into four portions."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "Put it on four plates."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "Mound up those four plates with vegetables"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "and then open up the very best bottle of Burgundy you have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "light the candles and celebrate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "Celebrate the opportunity you have to eat this."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "Invite your friends and neighbors over"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "and repeat once a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "maybe."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "I expect a lot from food."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "I expect health"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "and joy and family and community."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "I expect that producing ingredients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "preparing dishes and eating meals"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "is all part of the communion of human interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "I was lucky enough that my father was a fantastic cook."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "And he taught me very early on"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "about the privilege that eating represents."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "I remember well the meals of my childhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "They were reasonable portions of protein"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "served with copious quantities of vegetables"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "and small amounts of starch, usually rice."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "This is still how I largely eat today."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "I get sick when I go to steakhouses."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "I get the meat sweats."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like a hangover from protein."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 477260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s disgusting."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "But of all the dire news that you&#39;ll hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "and that you have heard about the state of our oceans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "I have the unfortunate burden of delivering to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "possibly the very worst of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "and that is this whole time"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "your mother was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "Eat your vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 494260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s pretty straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "So what are we looking for in a meal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "Well for health, I&#39;m looking for wholesome ingredients"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "that are good for my body."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "For joy, I&#39;m looking for butter and salt"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "and sexy things that make things taste less like penance."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 511260.0,
      "text": "For family, I&#39;m looking for recipes"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 511260.0,
      "end_time": 514260.0,
      "text": "that genuflect to my own personal histories."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "For community though, we start at the very beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no escaping the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 521260.0,
      "text": "that everything we eat has a global impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 521260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "So try and learn as best you can what that impact is"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 526260.0,
      "text": "and then take the first step to minimize it."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen an image of our blue planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 531260.0,
      "text": "our world bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 534260.0,
      "text": "But it is more than just a repository of our resources;"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also the global geography"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 537260.0,
      "end_time": 540260.0,
      "text": "of the communion we call dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 540260.0,
      "end_time": 542260.0,
      "text": "So if we all take only what we need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 542260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "then we can begin to share the rest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 547260.0,
      "text": "we can begin to celebrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 547260.0,
      "end_time": 549260.0,
      "text": "we can begin to restore."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 551260.0,
      "text": "We need to savor vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 551260.0,
      "end_time": 554260.0,
      "text": "We need to savor smaller portions of seafood."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 554260.0,
      "end_time": 556260.0,
      "text": "And we need to save dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 558260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}